node.text:
customized an iPad Pro for one of the voice actors of @pixarluca by @disney this week! 🧜‍♂️👀 
-
Didn’t want to post this to Instagram at first because it’s not my art style at all, but too many of y’all requested it ever since it got 40 million views on TikTok.. 🤯
-
@leomahalo 
-
#disney by #pixar and #pixarluca for #jackdylangrazer on #ipad in #doodle with #acrylicpainting plus #posca new #artoftheday
